===Noun===
'''toque''' or '''tuque''' ([[toques]]) French-Canadian Origin

#A Canadian term for a winter hat that is often a woolen, cotton, or acrylic, tightly knit triangular shaped hat with a small pom-pom affixed at the top.  Similar to military watch-cap.

